Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.44,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}本字幕由喵萌奶茶屋製作  僅供交流試看之用  請勿用於商業用途 \N\N翻譯: Oscuro　校對: Dysonsphere　繁化: 雲棋　後期: MIR
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,跑步好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒見到老爺爺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,機器狗也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,希望人沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那個老爺爺已經壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,壞掉了也能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定會神采奕奕地回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有慶典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,已經發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗎啡戒斷症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要給他吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一旦讓他吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前開著卡車亂闖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為過量攝入嗎啡所致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩人被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼還留他一命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在那孩子的生日慶典之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再出什麼亂子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺來接妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和我回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這個可憐的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了孫女的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,妳可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大地沒受傷真是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要隆重慶祝他的十歲生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝您的高額捐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我能優先享受儀式了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這要視天啟而定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你也只能這樣回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡我們也會金繕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說這是一處新裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,下面帶您參觀藏書閣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你很難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,又是眨眼和手指敲擊的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,摩斯電碼 我隨便打的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,摩斯電碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在打摩斯電碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的話眨眼一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的話眨眼兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是偶然眨了眨眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 我看不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂摩斯電碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你能再來一遍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,最好一個字一個字地來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,オ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還是オ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,キ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ナ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ジ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,シ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ク
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ル
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,コ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,コ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,キ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,ケ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,即將有大型地震到來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵達尼號 SOS 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是漁夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是的小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,與收容地的交涉正在推進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,隨機抽選的第一批人員開始轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有大地震要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以前也沒出過事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我去跟媽媽說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那個臥病在床的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是潛水艇的小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前不知道他為什麼老眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是摩斯電碼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他說有大地震要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們趕緊逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這讓人怎麼能不慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,得快點通知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,妳確定妳剛剛說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,步 我相信妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是小野寺先生的情報是否正確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,還需要進一步確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,切肉的菜刀是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是犯了什麼事被抓起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,請救救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大地震要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快點離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,別說這麼嚇人的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妳他媽胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,別毀了我們的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,地震根本預測不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不是很安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這是來自小野寺的準確情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小野寺又是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把他給老子帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是潛水艇駕駛員小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個說日本要沉沒的小野寺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那他人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這裡的療養大樓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡也很危險 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,火災
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是大麻起火燒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在這麼重要的日子裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個老不死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他媽的太痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我嗎啡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你這要完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這也太嚇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,難道巨像也要塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要這樣 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大谷叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,出醜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我把菜刀拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,剛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我雖然只是塊頭大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但也能派上用場對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,剛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個打假賽被除名的關取力士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經無處可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,剛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,請您抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,請帶大家離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要捨棄這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,打開大門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都他媽在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,給老子開門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把門撞開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你別擠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這些歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會交給你啊 真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妳還真敢打我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 是你打開金庫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都不把我放在眼裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你們又來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看來大家目的相同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,請逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一樓已經出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,走樓上出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子還在上面等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,人沒找到 但是鑰匙在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,葉惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,救救大地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.98,Top,,0,0,0,,謝 謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你孫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子不是你的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孫女被土石流沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望她在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你們快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想聽聽孫女的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以聽到我孫女的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你孫女讓我這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,菸也別抽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,說了不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快 上車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼爾也快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是普通的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是我的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想聽到那個人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直守望著你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再會了 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你會沒命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼跟剛交代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己去說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,給你 當是餞別了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,發現了 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老爺爺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快開車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,安全駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爺 爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,千萬別回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我這個母親當得真失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這裡他才能活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的最後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,或許就是希望妳不要召喚他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,請妳為了自己活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺他這樣說道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就必須活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是我們的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不能止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我們和妳在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我這條命都是妳給的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我和你們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要糟蹋自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳創造了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都被需要的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和大家一起邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是哪裡出錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的能力要為了這孩子而使用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世上沒有無用的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,創造一個這孩子也能獲得尊嚴的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是最後一張了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,火山活動已經穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:23:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,日本不會立即沉沒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家冷靜對待 不要做出過激行為
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不論去哪裡
